# Packaging Options

This projects uses a few packaging options:
- Nix Flakes (`flake.nix` and `default.nix`)
- Install Script (`install.sh`)
- Homebrew Formula (`Formula.rb`)
- PyPi (`pyproject.toml`)
- Container Images (`docker/`)
- Kubernetes helm Charts template (`charts/`)
- Kubernetes helm Charts application, which are using helm Charts template from (`charts/`) are in  (`applications/`)

These should be properly maintianed as the project experiences updates.
